Akfen Hires Credit Suisse for Possible TAV Stake Sale

-- B y   B e n j a m i n   H a r v e y
-- 
2011-09-28T15:38:23Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-28/akfen-hires-credit-suisse-for-possible-tav-stake-sale.html
Akfen Holding AS (AKFEN)  and Tepe Insaat
Sanayi AS hired Credit Suisse for a possible sale of a stake in
airport operator  TAV Havalimanlari Holding AS. (TAVHL)   Credit Suisse will help the companies assess strategic
options for TAV including a share sale, Akfen said in a filing
with the  Istanbul Stock Exchange  today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Benjamin Harvey in Istanbul at 
 bharvey11@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Mark Bentley at 
 mbentley3@bloomberg.net  